lead_paragraph: Bryson DeChambeau is the only golfer at the Masters with a set of irons that are all the same length. The last guy to try that was none other than Bobby Jones, the club's co-founder.

headline.print_headline: Masters Mad Scientist: Amateur's Unusual Clubs and Swing
